Class Pickup

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • main.java.questfortheabodeth.powerups.Pickup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, Collidable, Powerup, org.jsfml.graphics.Drawable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AmmoPickup, DamagePlus, HealthBoost, ShieldPickup, SpeedPickupUp, TheAbodeth

    public abstract class Pickup
extends java.lang.Thread
implements org.jsfml.graphics.Drawable, Powerup
    The base class for all pickups. Provides methods to draw the pickup on the screen and methods so that collision detection can be run on these objects so that they can be picked up.
